## Database Schema

Social login users are stored with special National ID formats:

| Login Method | National ID Format | Example |
|--------------|-------------------|---------|
| Regular | User-provided | `NP-1234-5678` |
| Google | `GOOGLE-{id}` | `GOOGLE-1234567890` |
| Facebook | `FB-{id}` | `FB-9876543210` |

